import * as React from "react" import * as Svg from "../Svg" import * as Db from "../data/Database" class DiningCard extends React.Component { render() { this.data = Db.dining_details[this.props.dining] this.data["title"] = this.props.dining return (
{this.data.title} {this.data.price}
{this.data.description}
{Svg.location(this.props.isLiked)} {this.data.location}
{Svg.star(!this.props.isLiked)}
) } } export default DiningCard
